manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 1200Mbps WiFi Extender with 2.4&5GHz Dual Band Are you often get frustrated because your room doesn't have Internet access? Now You can say goodbye to dead spots, buffering, and dropped calls. Get a strong WiFi signal throughout your home so you can stream, game, and work with confidence. Whether you live in a one-bedroom apartment or thousands square-feet mansion, Our 2023 Newest 12001200Mbps WiFi Repeater got you phone and computer accessed.

Say goodbye to Wi-Fi dead zones You must have these annoyances of following: weak signal in the bathroom, WiFi signal intermittent, weak signal through thick walls and so on. Whether you’re running a business, running to online class or simply streaming, this ​wireless WiFi extender can help you. Guaranteed to spread a satisfying internet across your devices.

How to set up? 1. Plug the extender into a power outlet near your router. Wait about 10s until the 5G LED turns solid on. 2. Go to the WiFi setting and select Repeater-XXXX to connect. (If you network does not support 5G, please select 2.4G to connect.) 3. After entering the administrator login interface, select the language to proceed to the next step. 4. Select Repeater Mode or AP Mode, then enter the password of your router to connect. 5. Set the extender SSID and password, or keep it the same. 6. Wait about 30s to complete the setting. Click Done and go back to WiFi setting. Select the extender SSID and enter the password you set with the extender. After it shows that the connection is successful, you can use it.
